Package ohos.wearable.tile

Class TileAnimationData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.wearable.tile.TileAnimationData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ohos.utils.Sequenceable

    public class TileAnimationData
extends java.lang.Object
implements ohos.utils.Sequenceable
    Provides information about a frame animation.

    A TileAnimationData object needs to be created if the TileAbility wants to add an animation to a tile via TileEntity.Builder#addAnimationData(TileAnimationData).
